data.description: Welcome to 1415 Fairmont Ave. This beautiful 4 bed 2 bath home is 2080 sqft and boast numerous updates.  The kitchen includes new countertops, flooring, cabinetry, and appliances. The new stamped concrete patio has space for grilling on one end and a place for a hot tub at the other, each side secluded with new vinyl fencing surround. The perfect place to enjoy the backyard! Other updates include light fixtures, paint, accent walls, upgraded electrical panel, hot tub wiring, bathroom flooring, new doors upstairs, and basement carpet.  Home has wood stove and AC to help with extreme weather. You won't want to miss this one!
